.container
  .section
    / Icon Section
    .row.center
      .col.s12.m4
        .icon-block
          %h2.center.brown-text
            %i.material-icons flash_on
          %h5.center Find Jobs
          %p.light Our scraper scrapes popular job boards to give you a clean and ad free listing of jobs.
      .col.s12.m4
        .icon-block
          %h2.center.brown-text
            %i.material-icons group
          %h5.center Filter Jobs
          %p.light Use our search tools to narrow your search to what you really want. 
      .col.s12.m4
        .icon-block
          %h2.center.brown-text
            %i.material-icons settings
          %h5.center Track Jobs
          %p.light Save Jobs. Track Jobs. Comment on Jobs. Our tool makes it east. The job search shoudln't suck.
